video.title: How to Get Away With Murder
video.synopsis: Brilliant criminal defense attorney and law professor Annalise Keating, plus five of her students, become involved in a twisted murder case.

episodes.synopsis: A tough criminal law professor challenges her brightest students to solve thorny cases, but five scholars soon learn the high price of impressing her.
episodes.title: Pilot

episodes.synopsis: Annalise challenges her students to prove the innocence of an eccentric millionaire suspected of his wife's murder; Wes may be harboring secrets.
episodes.title: It's All Her Fault

episodes.synopsis: A soccer mom arrested for a petty crime turns out to be a terrorist; Annalise represents a college football star linked to Lila's disappearance.
episodes.title: Smile, or Go to Jail

episodes.synopsis: Annalise and her students dig up a shocking truth when the head of a brokerage firm is arrested for insider trading; Wes discovers an unsettling clue.
episodes.title: Let's Get to Scooping

episodes.synopsis: Annalise represents a minor who shot his police officer father; Annalise and Sam argue over Lila; Wes and Rebecca question Annalise's motives.
episodes.title: We're Not Friends

episodes.synopsis: A case gets personal for Annalise and the team when their client is a man sentenced to death by Asher's father; Frank tries to find Rebecca.
episodes.title: Freakin' Whack-a-Mole

episodes.synopsis: When the judge enforces a gag order in Rebecca's case, she takes matters into her own hands; Michaela is surprised by a prenuptial agreement.
episodes.title: He Deserved to Die

episodes.synopsis: The team represents a woman on trial for killing her nanny; a shocking discovery in Lila's case tests loyalties; more is revealed about Sam and Lila.
episodes.title: He Has a Wife

episodes.synopsis: On the evening of the bonfire, future flashes finally sync with the present, and the exact circumstances of Sam's death are finally revealed.
episodes.title: Kill Me, Kill Me, Kill Me

episodes.synopsis: As the team helps Annalise search for Sam, it is unclear how much Annalise really knows; a surprise visitor makes things harder on the students.
episodes.title: Hello Raskolnikov

episodes.synopsis: As school resumes after winter break, the campus is abuzz over Sam's disappearance; while Hannah probes, Annalise focuses on a victim of spousal abuse.
episodes.title: Best Christmas Ever

episodes.synopsis: A shocking discovery in Sam's case changes everything for Annalise and the team; the students find themselves on a tricky case that involves the mob.
episodes.title: She's a Murderer

episodes.synopsis: Wracked with guilt, Annalise turns to an unlikely source for help; Bonnie is tasked with representing a new client accused of rape.
episodes.title: Mama's Here Now

episodes.synopsis: A priest is accused of killing another man of the cloth; suspicion grows between Wes and Rebecca; the pieces of Lila's murder start to fit together.
episodes.title: The Night Lila Died

episodes.synopsis: Wes, Michaela, Connor and Laurel find themselves caught in a bind before the truth about Lila's death can be brought to light.
episodes.title: It's All My Fault

episodes.synopsis: While the others reel from Rebecca's disappearance, Annalise and Frank keep the truth a secret and covertly try to find the culprit.
episodes.title: It's Time to Move On

episodes.synopsis: Annalise scrambles to defend her sibling clients against surprising new charges and, later, endures a grueling cross-examination.
episodes.title: She's Dying

episodes.synopsis: Annalise agrees to defend an elite sex club owner. Later, a damaging photograph casts fresh suspicion on her sibling clients accused of murder.
episodes.title: It's Called the Octopus

episodes.synopsis: Wes uncovers more details about Rebecca's disappearance, and Connor suffers a crisis of conscience defending a girl accused of murdering her friend.
episodes.title: Skanks Get Shanked

episodes.synopsis: While the team grows anxious about getting arrested, Wes probes further into Rebecca's disappearance and finds himself in a volatile situation.
episodes.title: Meet Bonnie

episodes.synopsis: Annalise defends a transgender professor against charges of murder, leaving the rest of the team to handle the increasingly tricky Hapstall case.
episodes.title: Two Birds, One Millstone

episodes.synopsis: Eve defends Nate against charges that he murdered his wife, and Annalise takes on a client accused of harassing someone into suicide.
episodes.title: I Want You to Die

episodes.synopsis: After Philip blackmails Annalise, new evidence reveals a shocking secret about his past. Catherine and Caleb ponder taking a plea deal.
episodes.title: Hi, I'm Philip

episodes.synopsis: When Sinclair's feud with Annalise reaches a dreadful climax, Annalise pressures one of the Keating 5 to cover up the incident.
episodes.title: What Did We Do?

episodes.synopsis: Annalise begins to recover but suffers from hallucinations. Meanwhile, Wes sets out to learn how Annalise knew his secret.
episodes.title: What Happened to You, Annalise?

episodes.synopsis: While Wes languishes in a psych ward, the group frets that he'll expose their secrets. Meanwhile, Annalise shares pieces of her past.
episodes.title: She Hates Us

episodes.synopsis: Annalise takes a risky gamble to thwart Philip's blackmailing scheme, and Wes hits the road to learn the truth about his mother's death.
episodes.title: It's a Trap

episodes.synopsis: Wes visits Eve for information about his mother's death. Annalise's desperate measures to stop Philip lead to a dangerous confrontation.
episodes.title: Something Bad Happened

episodes.synopsis: The new assistant district attorney questions the team about Emily Sinclair. Annalise confides in Wes about his mother.
episodes.title: There's My Baby

episodes.synopsis: After skipping town to dodge an arrest warrant, Annalise returns to reveal the serial killer's true identity. Wes learns the truth about his past.
episodes.title: Anna Mae

episodes.synopsis: In the aftermath of Wallace Mahoney's murder, Annalise creates a criminal law clinic allowing students to try their own pro bono cases.
episodes.title: We're Good People Now

episodes.synopsis: The students compete to take on the case of an abused woman who may have murdered her husband. Annalise pushes back against the university board.
episodes.title: There Are Worse Things Than Murder

episodes.synopsis: An unlikely source leads Laurel to a shocking discovery. Annalise involves her class in a high-profile murder case with a despicable defendant.
episodes.title: Always Bet Black

episodes.synopsis: A fateful slap comes back to haunt Annalise and puts her young client's case in serious jeopardy. Frank commits a bold act of vengeance.
episodes.title: Don't Tell Annalise

episodes.synopsis: Annalise confirms the source of the fliers branding her a "killer." A shocking discovery about the night of the fire changes everything.
episodes.title: It's About Frank

episodes.synopsis: While the team works to defend a veteran accused of assault, the police question Wes about his involvement in Wallace Mahoney's murder.
episodes.title: Is Someone Really Dead?

episodes.synopsis: Annalise takes on three siblings accused of conspiring to kill their mother. Wes lies to the police, and Frank's actions net serious consequences.
episodes.title: Call It Mother's Intuition

episodes.synopsis: When Wes receives a subpoena, Annalise turns to Frank for valuable information -- but tension flares between the two later on.
episodes.title: No More Blood

episodes.synopsis: Annalise learns she's under investigation, which sparks a relapse. The events leading up to the house fire unveil the person lying under the sheet.
episodes.title: Who's Dead?

episodes.synopsis: With Annalise in jail facing arson and first-degree murder charges, the D.A.'s office builds its case against her. Laurel is admitted to the hospital.
episodes.title: We're Bad People

episodes.synopsis: A jailed Annalise struggles to adapt to life behind bars. The fractured team learns that the investigation is much larger than they realized.
episodes.title: Not Everything's About Annalise

episodes.synopsis: Competing priorities keep the team from attending Annalise's hearing, but Annalise's parents show up at the trial, where tensions run high.
episodes.title: Go Cry Somewhere Else

episodes.synopsis: Annalise makes it her mission to take down the D.A.'s office. Meanwhile, Laurel hires a private investigator, and Frank fires his lawyer.
episodes.title: It's War

episodes.synopsis: Connor makes a stunning confession about his whereabouts on the night of the fire and offers to take the stand, but Annalise calls Laurel instead.
episodes.title: He Made a Terrible Mistake

episodes.synopsis: With pressure mounting from a variety of sources, Annalise confronts Sylvia Mahoney, and Laurel prepares to take matters into her own hands.
episodes.title: Wes

episodes.synopsis: Determined to turn over a new leaf, Annalise asks for another chance at her disbarment hearing and makes a surprising announcement to the Keating 4.
episodes.title: I'm Going Away

episodes.synopsis: Annalise finds evidence to help her client. Connor tries to mend fences with Laurel, who continues her investigation into her father.
episodes.title: I'm Not Her

episodes.synopsis: Laurel's request puts Michaela in a difficult position at her new job. Annalise takes on a new case, but the stakes are raised when Nate gets involved.
episodes.title: It's for the Greater Good

episodes.synopsis: Annalise gears up for the class action lawsuit and crosses paths with Michaela on a new case. Laurel connects the dots between Denver and Antares.
episodes.title: Was She Ever Good at Her Job?

episodes.synopsis: A suspicious Bonnie schemes to sabotage Annalise's lawsuit. Laurel and Michaela enlist Oliver's help in accessing a key document.
episodes.title: I Love Her

episodes.synopsis: Unexpected news about Antares heightens the stakes for Laurel, Michaela and Oliver. Annalise opens up to Dr. Roa about her painful past.
episodes.title: Stay Strong, Mama

episodes.synopsis: The attorney general takes his smear campaign against Annalise to court. Laurel's plan jeopardizes Michaela and Asher's relationship.
episodes.title: Nobody Roots for Goliath

episodes.synopsis: Bonnie confronts Annalise about her actual motives. Laurel's plan gets off on the wrong foot when someone unexpectedly overhears them.
episodes.title: Live. Live. Live

episodes.synopsis: With the fate of Laurel's baby on the line, Frank takes matters into his own hands. Bonnie pulls strings to help Asher.
episodes.title: He's Dead

episodes.synopsis: An old voicemail from Wes leads Frank, Annalise and Laurel to a new clue. Annalise calls on Bonnie for help locating a valuable piece of evidence.
episodes.title: Everything We Did Was for Nothing

episodes.synopsis: Annalise and Nate visit someone from his past. For the custody battle, Laurel and Annalise bring in a new witness who has secrets of her own.
episodes.title: He's a Bad Father

episodes.synopsis: Annalise chooses Nate's father as her first witness, but the case hits a roadblock. Dr. Roa reveals shocking details about Stella's death.
episodes.title: Ask Him About Stella

episodes.synopsis: Annalise takes her class action lawsuit to the Supreme Court, but on the day of the hearing, she's unsettled by a phone call regarding Dr. Roa.
episodes.title: Lahey v. Commonwealth of Pennsylvania

episodes.synopsis: Laurel and Frank confront Sandrine about the recording. Simon recalls details about the night of the party and hires a lawyer.
episodes.title: The Day Before He Died

episodes.synopsis: Michaela decides on her own way to silence Simon. In an evidence locker, Nate finds the one thing that can turn Laurel's life around.
episodes.title: Nobody Else Is Dying

episodes.synopsis: Annalise's job search hits a snag due to blowback from her class action lawsuit. Frank is suspicious of Gabriel and decides to look into his background.
episodes.title: Your Funeral

episodes.synopsis: Annalise prepares to defend her first class action client and wards off pressure from Emmett. Frank gains access to Gabriel's personal life.
episodes.title: Whose Blood Is That?

episodes.synopsis: As the governor tightens the screws, Annalise defends a CEO accused of murder. Asher complicates Bonnie and Miller's budding romance.
episodes.title: The Baby Was Never Dead

episodes.synopsis: Nate's revelations about Bonnie's child pose a dilemma for Annalise, who's preoccupied with Nate's dad's case. Oliver looks into Gabriel's history.
episodes.title: It's Her Kid

episodes.synopsis: As the stakes rise in Nate Sr.'s case, Gabriel asks Annalise to consider moving for a mistrial. Bonnie's wary of reopening old wounds.
episodes.title: It Was the Worst Day of My Life

episodes.synopsis: Governor Birkhead makes Annalise an enticing offer and promises to pardon Nate Sr. Frank finds out what Julie's been hiding from Bonnie.
episodes.title: We Can Find Him

episodes.synopsis: Blindsided by the governor's sleight of hand, Annalise pushes for an inquest of Nate Sr.'s incident. Tegan finds dirt on Emmett to help Annalise.
episodes.title: I Got Played

episodes.synopsis: From the warden's phone records, Nate identifies the person responsible for his dad's death. Frank tells Annalise about Gabriel at the wedding.
episodes.title: I Want to Love You Until the Day I Die

episodes.synopsis: Gabriel presses Annalise on how his father died. In a flashback, Sam tries to approach Vivian and get in touch with their son.
episodes.title: He Betrayed Us Both

episodes.synopsis: Nate and Bonnie scramble for a solid alibi. Eve, Frank and Annalise dig up information on Vivian to keep Gabriel from pursuing Sam's case.
episodes.title: Don't Go Dark on Me

episodes.synopsis: Agent Telesco questions Gabriel about a suspicious voicemail. Nate is determined to track down the doctored evidence presented at the inquest.
episodes.title: Be the Martyr

episodes.synopsis: Michaela finds a way to keep Tegan quiet. After charging him with domestic terrorism, the FBI tries to persuade Gabriel to cooperate with them.
episodes.title: We Know Everything

episodes.synopsis: Annalise mulls over Agent Telesco's offer of immunity, but Tegan makes an unexpected move. A shocking fact comes to light about Nate Sr.'s killer.
episodes.title: Where Are Your Parents?

episodes.synopsis: Agent Telesco agrees to help Laurel identify her mystery caller in exchange for information. Bonnie obtains footage of the man visiting Nate Sr.
episodes.title: Make Me the Enemy

episodes.synopsis: After Laurel and Annalise confront Xavier, the governor resorts to a different plan. Frank hides the truth about Miller from Bonnie and Nate.
episodes.title: Please Say No One Else Is Dead

episodes.synopsis: As Laurel's whereabouts remain unknown, Annalise makes a breakthrough in rehab and Nate grows suspicious of Tegan.
episodes.title: Say Goodbye

episodes.synopsis: Oliver helps Michaela track down her father, Frank scrambles to find a way into a safe deposit box and Connor defends a client seeking asylum.
episodes.title: Vivian's Here

episodes.synopsis: Michaela's case hits a snag, Vivian faces a crucial dilemma and Frank uncovers a clue that may bring him closer to Laurel.
episodes.title: Do You Think I'm a Bad Man?

episodes.synopsis: Tegan's firm takes on an anti-discrimination case, Nate suspects Tegan's link to Laurel's disappearance and Michaela's trip with Gabriel unravels.
episodes.title: I Hate the World

episodes.synopsis: Frank shares a secret about Laurel's disappearance, Michaela's dad draws her into his orbit and Tegan faces a dilemma in her divorce proceedings.
episodes.title: We're All Gonna Die

episodes.synopsis: Cora calls Nate's bluff. Annalise makes a deal with Solomon and petitions for a restraining order against the Castillos.
episodes.title: Family Sucks

episodes.synopsis: Gabriel is first chair in a restorative justice case. Annalise asks Frank to stop Tegan from filing a suit against the governor.
episodes.title: I'm the Murderer

episodes.synopsis: The students take on a hypothetical conspiracy-to-murder case, the governor takes the stand at Nate Sr.'s trial and peril awaits Bonnie.
episodes.title: I Want to Be Free

episodes.synopsis: Michaela receives an unexpected phone call, the identity of the FBI informant comes to light and tensions come to a head between Annalise and Nate.
episodes.title: Are You the Mole?

episodes.synopsis: In the wake of tragedy, Bonnie tells Oliver about Asher's visit the previous night and the FBI offers Michaela and Connor an ultimatum.
episodes.title: We're Not Getting Away With It

episodes.synopsis: Gabriel conceals key details behind Asher's death. Annalise asks to meet Connor and Michaela as her past catches up to her.
episodes.title: The Reckoning

episodes.synopsis: Gabriel makes a shocking revelation about Asher's real killer, Annalise faces a dire fate and Frank follows an FBI agent to someone unexpected.
episodes.title: Let's Hurt Him

episodes.synopsis: Vivian tells Annalise about Sam and Hannah's murky past. The FBI tightens the screws on Michaela and Connor.
episodes.title: What if Sam Wasn't the Bad Guy This Whole Time?

episodes.synopsis: Annalise and Bonnie blackmail Hannah with secrets about her past, a surprise witness appears at Annalise's trial and Nate convinces Jorge to testify.
episodes.title: Annalise Keating is Dead

episodes.synopsis: Annalise questions the governor, an unexpected testimony turns the tide in Annalise's favor and Frank makes a fateful decision.
episodes.title: Stay
